data.title: Combinatorics and Geometry Seminar
data.meta_description: UW Combinatorics and Geometry Seminar meets in Padelford C-401 on Wednesdays. The pre-seminar is from 3:30-4:00pm and the main seminar is from 4:10-5:00pm. Further details can be found at https://sites.math.washington.edu/~combinat/
data.text:
UW Combinatorics and Geometry Seminar meets in Padelford C-401 on Wednesdays. The pre-seminar is from 3:30-4:00pm and the main seminar is from 4:10-5:00pm.

Further details can be found at https://sites.math.washington.edu/~combinat/
